{"id":"5e9c09c5774c2610387e5180","artists":["5e9b69117a1236eccfeb2256"],"title":"New: Laurel Halo – Sunlight On The Faded","content":"<p>Following the release of her debut LP, ‘<em>Quarantine</em>’, on Hyperdub, <strong><a href=\"https://www.</p><p>facebook.com/laurelhalo\">Laurel Halo</a></strong> returns this month with her new single ‘<em>Sunlight On The Faded</em>’, which was premiered on Belgium radio station<strong> Scorpio</strong> last Friday. It’s a choppy and manic affair, <strong>Halo</strong>’s lush harmonies snap and jar with her eloquently chaotic beats and wild synths. Amongst the whirlwind however is a real sense of romanticism, ‘only the best memories stay’, she repeats, same tone, same amount of conviction every time she says it. The repetition is enough, this one’s a keeper.</p>\n<div><object width=\"480\" height=\"480\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" codebase=\"https://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"wmode\" value=\"opaque\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"//www.mixcloud.com/media/swf/player/mixcloudLoader.swf?feed=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mixcloud.com%2FSterrenplaten%2Flaurel-halo-sunlight-on-the-faded-sterrenplaten-30-november-2012%2F&embed_uuid=2d86a672-ff01-403f-932a-753d232aa59d&stylecolor=&embed_type=widget_standard\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><embed width=\"480\" height=\"480\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" src=\"//www.mixcloud.com/media/swf/player/mixcloudLoader.swf?feed=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mixcloud.com%2FSterrenplaten%2Flaurel-halo-sunlight-on-the-faded-sterrenplaten-30-november-2012%2F&embed_uuid=2d86a672-ff01-403f-932a-753d232aa59d&stylecolor=&embed_type=widget_standard\" allowFullScreen=\"true\" wmode=\"opaque\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" /></object></p>\n<div style=\"clear: both; height: 3px;\"></div>\